# Scripts entry points

All use `@hydra.main(config_path="../configs", config_name=...)`.

## train.py

- Config: `configs/train.yaml`
- Submitit/SLURM by default; local: `+launch_without_submitit=true`
- Resume: `+resume_run_id=<id>`, `+resume_mode=resume|fine_tune`
- Checkpoints under `paths.checkpoints/<run_id>`

## make_predictions.py

- Requires: `run_id`, `inference_cfg`, `split`
- Reloads experiment cfg from checkpoint; writes `paths.predictions/<run_id>/<pred_name>/`
- Multirun: `run_id=a,b,c` with `--multirun`

## eval.py

- `models` dict: `{DisplayName: [run_id, inference_cfg]}`
- `eval_class` list must match classes used at prediction time
- Optional: `+eval_name`, `checks_strictness=targets_only`

Example:

```bash
python scripts/train.py experiment=fm_ssl_M_w6h model=motif_12b_d512 setup=local \
  paths=local dataloader.batch_size=2 wandb.name=debug +launch_without_submitit=true +wandb.mode=disabled
```
